Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.55,TEXT-JP,,0,0,0,,じしょたんず!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:07.47,TEXT-JP,,0,0,0,,僕の体が光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.49,TEXT-JP,,0,0,0,,これは
